Package: HotellingEllipse
Title: Hotelling T-Square and Confidence Ellipse
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Christian L.",
           family = "Goueguel",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "christian.goueguel@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0521-3446"))
Description: The HotellingEllipse package is designed to help draw the Hotelling ellipse on the PCA or PLS score scatterplot. The package calculates the Hotelling's T-square value and provides the x-y coordinates of the Hotelling ellipse in addition to the length of the semi-minor and semi-major axes (a and b).
